{
  "stem": "4032.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we're treated a little better than the general population.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were Russian families, too, in-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For some reason, that they send them there for-- that I-- I really don't know why.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we worked hard, and we stayed there without knowing when the end will come.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, what-- what is the future bringing?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we worked there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were there 14 months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we heard that the General Sikorski, a Polish general, being in London forming a Polish government in London.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they'll take all the refugees all to the-- to form a Polish army and get out of the country, out of Russia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was very much interested in that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they released us from Siberia, and they said, you can go anyplace you want on your own.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Asia-- Russian Asia, like Uzbekistan, Turkestan, Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went in these parts of Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The situation-- economical station was there worse than in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were so many Russian refugees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that in the meantime, Germany attacked Russia in 1940-- I don't exactly remember the date.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the Germans were marching in with a speed till-- not far from Moscow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't exactly know, but they were-- they were saying they're very close to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then the Russians formed in the [INAUDIBLE] the-- the conditions in Russia, the-- the nature conditions in Russia were so good for the Russian people, that the German army froze to death.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were freezing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The soldiers-- the German soldiers were freezing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's when they had that fight under Stalingrad, which is in between Russia and-- in between Kiev and Moscow on the-- the Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
